Celgene Corp Announces Additional $3.0 Billion Share Repurchase Program
Wednesday, 12 Jun 2013 08:10am EDT
Celgene Corp announced that Board of Directors authorized the repurchase of up to an additional $3.0 billion of the Company`s common stock. Purchases may be made in the open market or in privately negotiated transactions from time to time, as determined by management and in accordance with applicable requirements of the Securities and Exchange Commission. Year-to-date, Celgene has repurchased approximately $1.8 billion of its common stock and has exhausted the previous $2.5 billion stock repurchase authorization. Celgene has repurchased approximately $6.5 billion of its common stock over the last four years.Â 
